    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后华尔街交易员纷纷退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wall-street-traders-rush-for-the-exit-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在引发金融市场大幅上涨近一年后，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔周三却做出了完全相反的举动，对 2025 年的降息持谨慎态度，令投资者感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wall-street-traders-rush-for-the-exit-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>成功集团表示，马来西亚资源公司退出高铁竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/malaysian-resources-exits-high-speed-rail-bid-berjaya-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据马来西亚资源公司 (Malaysia Resources Corp.) 的合作伙伴之一成功集团 (Berjaya Group) 透露，该公司已退出竞标吉隆坡和新加坡之间拟议的价值数十亿美元的高速铁路的财团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/malaysian-resources-exits-high-speed-rail-bid-berjaya-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
