      <title>东南亚股市有望在特朗普威胁下提供避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/southeast-asian-stocks-seen-offering-shelter-amid-trump-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了应对唐纳德·特朗普贸易政策的不确定性，全球投资者正将目光投向东南亚以寻求避风港，这将提振该地区股市明年的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/southeast-asian-stocks-seen-offering-shelter-amid-trump-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 23:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
